ivardefs.name: target
ivardefs.desc: A reference to the observation or [QuestionnaireResponse](questionnaireresponse.html#) resource that is related to this observation.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: A code specifying the kind of relationship that exists with the target resource.

properties.desc: A  reference to another resource (usually another Observation) whose relationship is defined by the relationship type code.
